trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner class provides signing functionality.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CmsSigner gir signering funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> class by using a default subject identifier type.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsSigner oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av en standard emne ID-type.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner> class has the following default property values.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner>klassen har følgende standardverdier for egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner>

trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> class with the specified cryptographic service provider (CSP) parameters.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsSigner oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> klassen med de angitte kryptografitjeneste (CSP provider).

trans-unit.source: CmsSigner is useful when you know the specific CSP and private key to use for signing.
trans-unit.target: CmsSigner er nyttig når du kjenner til bestemte CSP og private nøkkelen som brukes for signering.

trans-unit.source: For the default property values used with this constructor, see <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen standardverdiene brukes med denne konstruktøren, kan du se <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: An exception to those values when this constructor is used is that <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A> is set to <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Et unntak verdiene når denne konstruktøren brukes er som <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A>er satt til <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CspParameters"></xref> object that represents the set of CSP parameters to use.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CspParameters"> </xref> objektet som representerer settet med CSP parametere som brukes.

trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> class with the specified subject identifier type.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsSigner oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> klasse angitte emne ID-type.

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"></xref> enumeration that specifies the signer identifier type.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"> </xref> opplisting som angir signerer identifikator.

trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> class with the specified signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsSigner oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> klasse angitte signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: For the default property values used with this constructor, see <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen standardverdiene brukes med denne konstruktøren, kan du se <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: The signing certificate specified by the `certificate` parameter is not checked for validity on input.
trans-unit.target: Signeringssertifikatet angitt av den `certificate` parameteren er ikke kontrollert for gyldighetsperiode på inndataene.

trans-unit.source: To validate the certificate prior to supplying it to this constructor, use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: For å validere sertifikatet før du oppgir til denne konstruktøren, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"></xref> object that represents the signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"> </xref> objektet som representerer signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: The CmsSigner constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> class with the specified signer identifier type and signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CmsSigner oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> klassen med ID-type angitt som signerer og signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: The signing certificate specified by the `certificate` parameter is not checked for validity on input.
trans-unit.target: Signeringssertifikatet angitt av den `certificate` parameteren er ikke kontrollert for gyldighetsperiode på inndataene.

trans-unit.source: To validate the certificate prior to supplying it to this constructor, use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: For å validere sertifikatet før du oppgir til denne konstruktøren, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Chain.Build%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"></xref> enumeration that specifies the signer identifier type.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"> </xref> opplisting som angir signerer identifikator.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"></xref> object that represents the signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"> </xref> objektet som representerer signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: The Certificate property sets or retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"></xref> object that represents the signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen sertifikatet angir eller henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"> </xref> objektet som representerer signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"></xref> object that represents the signing certificate.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2"> </xref> objektet som representerer signeringssertifikatet.

trans-unit.source: The Certificates property retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref> collection that contains certificates associated with the message to be signed.
trans-unit.target: Sertifikater egenskapen henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"> </xref> samlingen som inneholder sertifikater som er forbundet med meldingen signeres.

trans-unit.source: This property may be used to hold certificates in the signer's certificate chain.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan brukes til å inneholde sertifikater i den signerer sertifikatkjeden.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the certificates included in the collection are determined by the setting of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet sertifikater som er inkludert i samlingen bestemmes av innstillingen for den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.IncludeOption%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not all certificates in the signer's certificate chain are necessarily present in Certificates.
trans-unit.target: Ikke alle sertifikater i den signerer sertifikatkjeden finnes nødvendigvis i sertifikater.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref> collection that represents the collection of certificates associated with the message to be signed.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"> </xref> samling som representerer samlingen av sertifikater som er forbundet med meldingen signeres.

trans-unit.source: The DigestAlgorithm property sets or retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> that represents the hash algorithm used with the signature.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen DigestAlgorithm angir eller henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"> </xref> som representerer hash-algoritmen som brukes med signatur.

trans-unit.source: For the default value of this property, see <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien for denne egenskapen, kan du se <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner.%23ctor>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"></xref> object that represents the hash algorithm used with the signature.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Oid"> </xref> objektet som representerer hash-algoritmen som brukes med signatur.

trans-unit.source: The IncludeOption property sets or retrieves the option that controls whether the root and entire chain associated with the signing certificate are included with the created CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IncludeOption angir eller henter alternativet som kontrollerer om root og hele kjeden som er knyttet til signeringssertifikatet er inkludert i opprettet CMS/PKCS #7 meldingen.

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption"></xref> enumeration that specifies how much of the X509 certificate chain should be included in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption"> </xref> opplisting som angir hvor mye X509 sertifikatkjeden må være inkludert i den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsSigner"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The IncludeOption property can be one of the following <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption"></xref> members.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IncludeOption kan være én av følgende <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509IncludeOption"> </xref> medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: Name
trans-unit.target: Navn

trans-unit.source: Value Meaning
trans-unit.target: Verdi betydning

trans-unit.source: 0 The certificate chain is not included.
trans-unit.target: 0 sertifikatkjeden er ikke inkludert.

trans-unit.source: 1 The certificate chain, except for the root certificate, is included.
trans-unit.target: 1 sertifikatkjeden, unntatt root-sertifikatet er inkludert.

trans-unit.source: 2 Only the end certificate is included.
trans-unit.target: 2 bare sluttsertifikatet er inkludert.

trans-unit.source: 3 The certificate chain, including the root certificate, is included.
trans-unit.target: 3 sertifikatkjeden, inkludert root-sertifikatet er inkludert.

trans-unit.source: One of the arguments provided to a method was not valid.
trans-unit.target: Ett av argumentene angitt til metoden er ikke gyldig.

trans-unit.source: The SignedAttributes property retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection of signed attributes to be associated with the resulting <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> content.
trans-unit.target: SignedAttributes egenskapen henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"> </xref> samling signerte attributter som skal knyttes til den resulterende <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> innhold.

trans-unit.source: Signed attributes are signed along with the specified content.
trans-unit.target: Signerte attributter er logget sammen med det angitte innholdet.

trans-unit.source: An example of a signed attribute that might be included in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection> collection retrieved by the SignedAttributes property is the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9SigningTime> signing time attribute.
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel på en signert attributt som kan inkluderes i den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection>samlingen hentet av egenskapen SignedAttributes den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9SigningTime>logger time-attributtet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9SigningTime> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType> object and a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9MessageDigest> object will be automatically generated and placed in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property for the corresponding signer whenever the SignedAttributes property is not empty.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType>objekt og en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9MessageDigest>objektet blir automatisk generert og er plassert i den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen for den tilsvarende som har signert når egenskapen SignedAttributes er tom.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo.SignedAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9MessageDigest> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9ContentType>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection that represents the signed attributes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"> </xref> samling som representerer de signerte attributtene.

trans-unit.source: If there are no signed attributes, the property is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes ingen signerte attributter, er egenskapen en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: The SignerIdentifierType property sets or retrieves the type of the identifier of the signer.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SignerIdentifierType angir eller henter av identifikatoren for den som signert.

trans-unit.source: A member of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"></xref> enumeration that specifies the type of the identifier of the signer.
trans-unit.target: Et medlem av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SubjectIdentifierType"> </xref> opplisting som angir identifikatoren for den som signert.

trans-unit.source: One of the arguments provided to a method was not valid.
trans-unit.target: Ett av argumentene angitt til metoden er ikke gyldig.

trans-unit.source: The UnsignedAttributes property retrieves the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection of unsigned PKCS #9 attributes to be associated with the resulting <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"></xref> content.
trans-unit.target: UnsignedAttributes egenskapen henter den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"> </xref> samling usignerte PKCS #9 attributter som skal knyttes til den resulterende <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.SignerInfo"> </xref> innhold.

trans-unit.source: Unsigned attributes can be modified without invalidating the signature.
trans-unit.target: Usignerte attributter kan endres uten at signaturen.

trans-unit.source: An example of an unsigned attribute that might be included in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection> collection retrieved by the UnsignedAttributes property is a countersignature.
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel på en usignert attributt som kan inkluderes i den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection>samlingen hentet av egenskapen UnsignedAttributes er en Medsignaturen.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection that represents the unsigned attributes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"> </xref> samling som representerer usignerte attributtene.

trans-unit.source: If there are no unsigned attributes, the property is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes ingen usignerte attributter, er egenskapen en tom samling.
